summary: Just a house.  Owned by a hunter,  he died and left the deed to you!  You don\\\'t know who this man is or do you.
descriptionHtml:
A simple house mod.  The house is located near Whiterun.  THe man who previously owned was killed by bandits.  He left the deed of the home to you.  This home has an Enchanting Table, Chests to store you gear, A kitchen and a nice cozy fire.  This house will have more to it in the future, perhaps a quest... hmmmm.  If you want this house to be part a bigger quest mod please tell me in the comments.  The file for the house will be up soon and there will be pictures. 

***********************************************************************************************
Thanks to Bethesda for Skyrim and Creation Kit.
